---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Director's Message — Knowledge IAS Academy">
  <section class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 pt-16 lg:pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[50%] h-[80%] bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top_right,rgba(245,166,35,0.12),transparent_70%)] -z-10"></div>
    <div data-reveal>
      <span class="chip"><span class="dot"></span>Director's Message</span>
      <h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-tight">
        <span class="gold-underline-animated">To all aspiring</span><br /><span class="italic text-[var(--color-ink-soft)]">Civil Servants.</span>
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 pb-20 prose-readable">
    <p>
      Embarking on the journey towards the Civil Services Examination is a monumental endeavor that requires meticulous preparation and steadfast dedication. As you navigate through your academic journey, it's never too early to start laying the foundation for success in the UPSC examinations. Beginning your preparation during your school days not only provides you with ample time to absorb key concepts but also allows you to develop essential skills gradually.
    </p>
    <p>
      By incorporating UPSC exam preparation into your daily routine from an early age, you can build a strong understanding of fundamental subjects and concepts. Start by familiarising yourself with the exam syllabus and structure, and gradually integrate relevant topics into your study schedule. Engage with a diverse range of reading materials — from textbooks to newspapers — to broaden your knowledge base and stay updated on current affairs.
    </p>
    <p>
      By starting your preparation early and adopting a holistic approach to learning, you pave the way for a rewarding and fulfilling journey towards achieving your dreams of serving the nation.
    </p>

    <blockquote class="my-12 border-l-4 border-[var(--color-gold)] bg-[var(--color-gold-soft)]/40 px-6 py-6 rounded-r-xl not-italic">
      <p class="font-serif text-xl sm:text-2xl leading-snug text-[var(--color-ink)]">
        “FOCUS SCHOOL is the perfect launchpad for future aspirations in public service and leadership. Join us on this transformative journey towards realising your dreams of serving the nation with integrity and excellence.”
      </p>
    </blockquote>

    <p>
      <strong>FOCUS SCHOOL</strong> is our specialised course designed for ambitious school students aspiring to embark on a successful journey towards the UPSC exams in the future. Tailored to suit the needs of young minds, this comprehensive programme not only provides a solid foundation in the core subjects of UPSC but also instills essential skills such as critical thinking, analytical reasoning, and effective communication.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our experienced faculty — comprising seasoned educators and UPSC experts — are dedicated to nurturing the potential of each student, guiding them through every step of their preparation. Empowering students with the knowledge, skills, and confidence they need to excel in one of the toughest exams in the country, our course is the perfect launchpad for their future aspirations in public service and leadership.
    </p>
    <p>
      Wishing you the best of luck on your UPSC journey!
    </p>

    <div class="mt-14 flex items-center gap-5">
      <div>
        <img src="/gallery/WhatsApp%20Image%202026-06-25%20at%2011.42.19%20AM.jpeg" alt="Ajay Sah" class="h-40 w-40 rounded-full object-cover" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-serif text-xl leading-none">Ajay Sah</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">Director, Knowledge IAS Academy</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-14">
      <a href="/focus-school" class="btn-primary">Discover FOCUS SCHOOL</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
